{"name":"Thorne D3+K2","price":"~$18","rating":"4.9","stars":5,"reviews":"12,000+","desc":"The perfect pair in one capsule — 1000 IU D3 and 200mcg K2 (MK-4). NSF Certified. Take 2 for a full 2000 IU D3 / 200mcg K2 dose. Arguably the single best bone health supplement available.","pros":["D3+K2 combo","NSF Certified","Clean formula","Easy dosing"],"cons":["K2 in MK-4 form (not MK-7)"],"best_for":"Core bone protocol"},
{"name":"Garden of Life mykind Organics Calcium","price":"~$30","rating":"4.6","stars":5,"reviews":"5,000+","desc":"Plant-based whole food calcium with D3, K2, and magnesium. Vegan certified. Comprehensive bone support from food-based sources with better absorption than synthetic blends.","pros":["Whole food sources","Vegan certified","Complete formula","Organic"],"cons":["More capsules per dose","Pricier"],"best_for":"Vegan bone health"},
